During upgrade from 4.1 to 4.3 RC1 User Directory configuration is not recreated from osuser.xml file when java.naming.security.principal parameter is commented (Parameter is commented by default when authentication to LDAP is not required). If is not commented everything is all right.
{code} 
<!-- Initial search is anonymous
     <property name="java.naming.security.principal"></property>
     <property name="java.naming.security.credentials"></property>
     -->
{code}
With errormessage :
{noformat}
JIRA is unable to migrate the User Directory configuration because the ldap configuration in the osuser.xml does not contain the parameter java.naming.security.principal.Please see the Upgrade Guide for details.
{noformat}

